      <title>对冲基金经理 Greg Coffey 寻找新的火鸡交易机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/hedge-fund-manager-greg-coffey-hunts-for-new-turkey-trades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，宏观交易员兼对冲基金经理格雷格·科菲 (Greg Coffey) 正在寻找投资土耳其的新理由，并于最近几周访问了土耳其进行会谈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/hedge-fund-manager-greg-coffey-hunts-for-new-turkey-trades</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 08:45:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
