      <title>贝莱德和大亨支持的杨忠礼集团将收购新加坡服务式公寓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/blackrock-tycoon-backed-ytl-set-to-buy-singapore-serviced-units-from-capitaland</link>
